          <detaileddescription>
<para>Name &quot;offsetPolicy&quot;, type Vector2 or Property::ARRAY of Property::STRING. If Property::ARRAY then 2 strings expected for the x and y.</para>
<para>C++: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">control.SetProperty(<sp/>...,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Some<sp/>visual<sp/>based<sp/>property</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
