<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Property::Array().Add(</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Visual_1_1Transform_1_1Property_1a2780ef129eb899ad62cf68b304d76080af4c513e0602261722dd988c65635c2bb" kindref="member">Ui::Visual::Transform::Property::OFFSET_POLICY</ref>,<sp/>Vector2(<sp/><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Visual_1_1Transform_1_1Policy_1a066960f7c22e9886b45d0480e7efb968aaf60f84f565b77e5c84cf136cb57ccfd" kindref="member">Policy::ABSOLUTE</ref>,<sp/><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Visual_1_1Transform_1_1Policy_1a066960f7c22e9886b45d0480e7efb968ad5cb718c26433cafef1458635f61510d" kindref="member">Policy::RELATIVE</ref><sp/>)<sp/>)<sp/>)<sp/>.Add(</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Visual_1_1Transform_1_1Property_1a2780ef129eb899ad62cf68b304d76080a698f6a176f2e2a1de21e0e4165203b29" kindref="member">Ui::Visual::Transform::Property::OFFSET</ref>,<sp/>Vector2(<sp/>10,<sp/>1.0f<sp/>)<sp/>)<sp/>);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>JSON: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;transition&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;offsetPolicy&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>:<sp/>[<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;ABSOLUTE&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;RELATIVE&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>],</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;offset&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>:<sp/>[<sp/>10,<sp/>1.0<sp/>]</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> <simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Visual_1_1Transform_1_1Policy_1a066960f7c22e9886b45d0480e7efb968" kindref="member">Policy::Type</ref> </para>
